sp.p:
I ſaw the Letters at St. Omers in the month of January;
then they came from Rome; and after I received ſummons to be at
this Conſult in the month of April; and accordingly we came over.

div.p:
Now this plainly ſhews, that our Religion was to be ſubverted,
Popery eſtabliſhed, and the three Kingdoms to be converted;
that is indeed, to be brought to confuſion.
